Contact Details: Author: Community and Mental Health team, NHS Digital Responsible Statistician: Paul Jennings, Principal Information Analyst Public Enquiries: 0300 303 5678 Email: enquiries@nhsdigital.nhs.uk
Description: These statistics describe patient outcomes in IAPT in terms of courses of therapy given. They supplement the 2018-19 annual Psychological Therapies publication.
Name: Psychological Therapies, Annual report on the use of IAPT services 2018-19
Notes: There are a number of  spreadsheets available on the landing page aas well as Power BI.  (IAPT) = Improving Access to Psychological Therapies  programme
Route from landing page to data: Data can be found by clicking on the link under latest version on the landing page, the metadata is available as a XLS spreadsheet  and a further 2 XLS and 1 CSV spreadsheet is available under resources.  additionally a rar file is available which may be better.
Sizing Notes: There are a number tables with footnotes, complex data, dimensions and sub dimensions so may need a bit of up front work required to determine dimensions. This may be better suited to the mental health family.
